# TC-23a — Work Calendar / Pay Period Foundation

## Purpose

Establish the foundational operational calendar and pay-period framework used by:

- employee time tracking
- weekly timesheets
- overtime calculation
- leave workflows
- payroll preparation
- payroll exports/imports
- Team360 payroll visibility
- operational payroll reporting

TC-23a defines shared operational workforce-period semantics for employee payroll workflows before downstream Phase 5 implementation begins.

TC-23a intentionally remains lightweight and operational in scope. TeamCORE is not a payroll tax engine or accounting platform.

---

